Interface CryptoService<T extends AuthenticationCredentials,U extends KeyConfig>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AmazonCloudHsmCryptoService, AzureKeyVaultCryptoService, BCCryptoService, GemaltoLunaCryptoService, JCACryptoService, SecurosysPrimusXCryptoService, UtimacoCryptoService

    public CryptoService<T extends AuthenticationCredentials,U extends KeyConfig>

    Crypto service that encompasses certain cryptographic operations such as signing of data.
